    /////////////    
    section#about.container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2 
          h2.section-heading About   
          h4.section-subheading Silicon Beach Sports League         
          p The Silicon Beach Sports League provides an environment for company employees, investors, and other entrepreneurs in Los Angeles to build connections in a startup community committed to staying fit. The League organizes tournaments and scrimmages for multiple sports including soccer, volleyball, ultimate frisbee, basketball, golf, and dodgeball.

